The VOC emissions module is already fully ported and committed (commit `52c9511`). Here's a summary of what's in place:

**Source file**: `src/biogeochem/voc_emission.jl` (837 lines)

**Types ported:**
- `MEGANFactors` — compound class parameters (Agro, Amat, Anew, Aold, betaT, ct1, ct2, Ceo, LDF)
- `MEGANCompound` — single MEGAN compound descriptor
- `MEGANMechComp` — mechanism compound mapping
- `VOCEmisData` — VOC emission state/flux data

**Functions ported:**
- `vocemis_init!` / `vocemis_clean!` — allocation/deallocation
- `megan_factors_init!` — default MEGAN factors setup
- `get_map_EF` — mapped isoprene emission factors by PFT group
- `get_gamma_P` — PPFD activity factor (sun/shade, calculated/fixed alpha/cp)
- `get_gamma_L` — LAI activity factor
- `get_gamma_SM` — soil moisture activity factor (Wang et al., 2022)
- `get_gamma_T` — temperature activity factor (incl. boreal shrub/grass updates)
- `get_gamma_A` — leaf age activity factor
- `get_gamma_C` — CO2 activity factor (Heald et al., 2009)
- `voc_emission!` — main driver

**Tests**: `test/test_voc_emission.jl` — covers all helper functions and driver integration. All 11,995 tests in the full suite pass.
